00:42:16.620 --> 00:42:20.057
empathetic and considerate and
is a really, really, really

00:42:20.057 --> 00:42:20.640
good listener.

00:42:20.640 --> 00:42:23.580
When he gets frustrated,
his passion might take over

00:42:23.580 --> 00:42:27.270
and he goes what I call Full Ye.

00:42:27.270 --> 00:42:30.180
But he has a heart of
gold, and he really

00:42:30.180 --> 00:42:32.890
