new office in Santa Monica.

00:52:30.904 --> 00:52:34.150
So we thought coming out
here was going to take hours.

00:52:34.150 --> 00:52:38.187
So I don't really have anything
to do for another hour.

00:52:38.187 --> 00:52:40.770
And Zach has my phone, so I have
no idea how many clients have

00:52:40.770 --> 00:52:41.822
called while I'm up here.

00:52:41.822 --> 00:52:43.530
And I'm actually really
enjoying the fact

00:52:43.530 --> 00:52:44.910
that I don't have a phone.

00:52:44.910 --> 00:52:48.174
This is like when I
went to Burning Man.

00:52:48.174 --> 00:52:49.590
JESSE MICHELS:
Google Burning Man.

00:52:49.590 --> 00:52:49.980
SCOOTER BRAUN: Yeah.

00:52:49.980 --> 00:52:50.970
JESSE MICHELS: Do
you have anything--

00:52:50.970 --> 00:52:51.930
SCOOTER BRAUN: This
is nothing like when

00:52:51.930 --> 00:52:52.846
I went to Burning Man.

00:52:55.052 --> 00:52:56.760
JESSE MICHELS: They
do say Burning Man is

00:52:56.760 --> 00:52:59.490
the new Davos though, like
it's all just tech execs.

00:52:59.490 --> 00:53:00.000
SCOOTER BRAUN: I liked it.

00:53:00.000 --> 00:53:00.875
I rode a bike around.

00:53:00.875 --> 00:53:01.672
I don't do drugs.

00:53:01.672 --> 00:53:04.130
And for those people who have
this stigma that you do drugs

00:53:04.130 --> 00:53:05.530
at Burning Man, not true.

00:53:05.530 --> 00:53:08.130
I don't do drugs,
but I do ride bikes.

00:53:08.130 --> 00:53:09.840
And I rode a bike
around that desert

00:53:09.840 --> 00:53:12.480
like I was 15 years old
at Bible Street Park.

00:53:12.480 --> 00:53:13.560
My phone wasn't on.

00:53:13.560 --> 00:53:14.730
I was a wild man.

00:53:14.730 --> 00:53:17.160
I was riding that thing
straight into oblivion,

00:53:17.160 --> 00:53:18.160
and it was awesome.

00:53:18.160 --> 00:53:20.039
So if you like
bike riding, I will

00:53:20.039 --> 00:53:21.330
tell you there's a great trail.

00:53:21.330 --> 00:53:22.330
It's called Burning Man.

