00:53:32.870 --> 00:53:33.870
SCOOTER BRAUN: I'm good.

00:53:33.870 --> 00:53:35.070
You guys are Google.

00:53:35.070 --> 00:53:36.403
You don't need anything from me.

00:53:36.403 --> 00:53:38.117
You've got a tea
shop in your office.

00:53:38.117 --> 00:53:41.197
[LAUGHTER]

